data.title: 以 3 到 5 分钟描写以下主题
data.content: What is important to you today that wasn't important to you 5 years ago? Explain why it's important to you now.
data.answer: I am a lead singer in the school band. I was always awed by the dilly fame and tempting compliments. But now being in the same boat, being a well-known feature in my university, these things seem shallow and not satisfactory. They have given me a great experience and a scintillating time to cherish but that’s not what important now. In all the rush and competition of being the best on stage and being admired, I missed out on a lot of things. The most important thing to me now is spending time with my own team more and enjoying the performances rather than sulking for results. （109 字）
